Package ie.atu.sw.util

Interface WordEmbeddingMapInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
WordEmbeddingMap
public interface WordEmbeddingMapInterface
Interface defining the structure and operations for managing a map of word embeddings. Provides methods to retrieve word embeddings, their associated words, and general information about the collection.
